rows.label: tlk70000063_02_msg0001
rows.name:
Hello, you lot! How's the ether
miasma removal coming along?

rows.label: tlk70000063_02_msg0002
rows.name:
If the evidence supports my theory,
I plan on presenting it at an academic
conference somewhere. But where?

rows.label: tlk70000063_02_msg0003
rows.name:
Superbia is the leading nation in
Alst, but Invidia's got a more
distinguished history and culture...

rows.label: tlk70000063_02_msg0004
rows.name:
Oooh, but what about Iira? The
birthplace of modern technology!
What I wouldn't give to present there.

rows.label: tlk70000063_02_msg0005
rows.name:
I'll try not to get too far ahead of
myself... It's all well and good to
dream, but I need to continue my research!
